headline: IT Services & Consulting Q2 Earnings: EPAM (NYSE:EPAM) Simply the Best
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at it services & consulting stocks, starting with EPAM (NYSE:EPAM).
